\c 7
\s Kusatenda kwavanun'una vaJesu
\p
\v 1 Shure kwezvinhu izvi Jesu wakafamba muGarirea; nokuti wakanga asingadi kufamba muJudhiya, nokuti vaJudha vakanga vachitsvaka kumuuraya.
\v 2 Zvino mutambo wavaJudha wamatumba wakanga wava pedo.
\p
\v 3 Naizvozvo vanun'una vake vakati kwaari: Ibvai pano muende Judhiya, kuti vadzidzi venyu vaonewo mabasa enyu amunoita.
\v 4 Nokuti hakuna munhu unoita chinhu muchivande kana iye amene achitsvaka kuzikamwa pachena. Kana iwe uchiita zvinhu izvi, zviratidze kunyika.
\v 5 Nokuti kunyange navanun'una vake vakanga vasingatendi kwaari.
\v 6 Naizvozvo Jesu akati kwavari: Nguva yangu ichigere kusvika, asi nguva yenyu inogara yakagadzirwa.
\v 7 Nyika haingakuvengiyi imwi; asi ini inondivenga, nokuti ndinopupura nezvayo, kuti mabasa ayo akaipa.
\v 8 Kwirai imwi kumutambo uyu; ini handisati ndokwira kumutambo, nokuti nguva yangu ichigere kuzadzisika.
\v 9 Wakati areva zvinhu izvozvi kwavari akagara muGarirea.
\s Jesu pamutambo wamatumba
\p
\v 10 Asi vanun'una vake vakati vakwira, iye pachakevo akabva okwira kumutambo, asingaendi pachena, asi panenge sapakavanda.
\v 11 Zvino vaJudha vakamutsvaka pamutambo, vakati: Uripiko iye?
\v 12 Kun'u'nuna kukuru kukavapo pakati pechaunga pamusoro pake, vamwe vachiti: Wakanaka; asi vamwe vachiti: Kwete, asi unotsausa chaunga.
\v 13 Kunyange zvakadaro kwakanga kusinomunhu waitaura pachena pamusoro pake nokutya vaJudha.
\v 14 Zvino kwakati pava pakati pomutambo, Jesu akakwira kutembere, akadzidzisa.
\v 15 Naizvozvo vaJudha vakashamiswa vachiti: Munhu uyu unoziva seiko magwaro asina kumbodzidza?
\v 16 Jesu akavapindura akati: Dzidziso yangu haizi yangu, asi yake wakandituma.
\v 17 Kana munhu achida kuita kuda kwake, uchaziva zvedzidziso kana ichibva kunaMwari, kana kuti ndinotaura zvemusoro wangu.
\v 18 Uyo unozvitaurira nezvake, unotsvaka kurumbidzwa kwake; asi unotsvaka kurumbidzwa kowakamutuma, ndiye wechokwadi, hapana kusarurama maari.
\p
\v 19 Mozisi haana kukupai murairo here? Asi hakunomumwe wenyu unochengeta murairo. Munotsvakireiko kundiuraya?
\v 20 Chaunga chikapindura chikati: Unomweya wakaipa iwe; ndianiko unotsvaka kukuuraya?
\v 21 Jesu akapindura akati kwavari: Ndakaita basa rimwe, mukashamiswa mose.
\v 22 Naizvozvo Mozisi wakakupai dzingiso, (kusiri kuti ndeyaMozisi, asi yamadzibaba), zvino imwi nemusi wesabata munodzingisa munhu.
\v 23 Zvino kana munhu achigamuchira dzingiso nesabata, kuti murairo waMozisi urege kuputswa, ko imwi monditsamwira nokuti ndaporesa munhu zvakakwana nemusi wesabata here?
\v 24 Musatonga nezvinoonekwa, asi tongai kutonga kwakarurama.
\p
\v 25 Naizvozvo vamwe vaveJerusarema vakati: Ko haazi iye wavanotsvaka kuuraya here?
\v 26 Asi tarirai, unotaura pachena vasingarevi chinhu kwaari. Ko vakuru vanoziva kwazvo here kuti ndiye Kristu?
\v 27 Zvino uyu tinoziva kwaanobva; asi Kristu kana achisvika, hakunomunhu ungaziva kwaanobva.
\v 28 Zvino Jesu akadanidzira mutembere achidzidzisa achiti: Imwi mose munondiziva, uye imwi mose munoziva kwandakabva; handina kuuya zvomusoro wangu, asi wakandituma ndowechokwadi, wamusingazivi imwi.
\v 29 Asi ini ndinomuziva, nokuti ndinobva kwaari, uye ndiye wakandituma.
\p
\v 30 Naizvozvo vakatsvaka kumubata, asi hakuna munhu wakaisa ruoko paari, nokuti nguva yake yakanga isati yasvika.
\v 31 Asi vazhinji vechaunga vakatenda kwaari, vakati: Kana Kristu achizosvika, ungaita zvishamiso zvizhinji kune zvizvi zvakaitwa nouyu here.
\v 32 Zvino vaFarisi vakanzwa vanhu vazhinji vachin'un'una zvinhu zvakadaro pamusoro pake; vaFarisi navapristi vakuru vakatuma vatariri kundomubata.
\v 33 Ipapo Jesu akati kwavari: Ndichiri nemwi chinguvana, ndoenda kunowakandituma.
\v 34 Imwi muchanditsvaka mukasa\add ndi\add*wana; uye apo pandiri, imwi hamungasviki\add po\add*.
\v 35 Zvino vaJudha vakati pakati pavo: Unoda kuendepiko kwatisingazomuwani? Ko unoda kuenda kuna vakapararira pakati pavaGiriki, adzidzise vaGiriki here?
\v 36 Ishokoiko iri raanoti: Muchanditsvaka, asi hamunga\add ndi\add*wani, nepandiri, imwi hamungasviki?
\v 37 Zvino nezuva rokupedzisira, iro guru romutambo, Jesu wakasimuka akadanidzira achiti: Kana ani nani anenyota, ngaauye kwandiri amwe.
\p
\v 38 Unotenda kwandiri, sezvakarehwa norugwaro, mudumbu make muchaerera nzizi dzemvura mhenyu.
\v 39 Asi izvi wakareva zvoMweya, waizogamuchirwa navo vaitenda kwaari, nokuti Mweya Mutsvene wakanga asati \add avapo\add*, nokuti Jesu wakanga asati akudzwa.
\p
\v 40 Naizvozvo vazhinji vechaunga vakati vachinzwa shoko iri vakati: Zvirokwazvo uyu muporofita.
\v 41 Vamwe vakati: Uyu ndiye Kristu. Asi vamwe vakati: Ko Kristu ungabva Garirea here?
\v 42 Rugwaro haruna kureva here kuti Kristu uchabva kuzvizvarwa zvaDhavhidhi, napamusha weBhetirehemu paiva naDhavhidhi?
\v 43 Naizvozvo pakava nekupesana pakati pechaunga pamusoro pake.
\v 44 Vamwe vavo vakanga vachida kumubata, asi kwakanga kusina wakaisa mavoko kwaari.
\p
\v 45 Zvino vatariri vakauya kuvapristi vakuru nokuvaFarisi; ivo vakati kwavari: Nemhaka yei musina kuuya naye?
\v 46 Vatariri vakapindura \add vakati\add*: Hakuna munhu wakatongotaura somunhu uyu.
\v 47 Zvino vaFarisi vakavapindura, \add vakati\add*: Nemwivo matsauswa kanhi?
\v 48 Kunomumwe wavakuru nowavaFarisi wakatongotenda kwaari here?
\v 49 Asi chaunga ichi chisingazivi murairo chakatukwa.
\v 50 Nikodhimo, uya akauya kwaari usiku, ari mumwe wavo, akati kwavari:
\v 51 Murairo wedu unotonga munhu usati wambomunzwa nokuziva chaanoita here?
\v 52 Vakapindura vakati kwaari: Ko newevo uri weGarirea here? Nzvera, uone kuti hakuna kumuka muporofita, unobva Garirea.
\v 53 Ipapo mumwe nomumwe wakaenda kumba kwake.
